GoodRx Helps is thrilled to announce Frieda Bequeaith as our next recipient of the Students for Healthcare Equity Scholarship. Frieda’s journey into reproductive health was sparked by a pivotal summer spent shadowing a midwife. Reflecting on that experience, Frieda shared, “Seeing how she connected with and supported her patients during those really crucial moments of fear and anxiety and joy and transition, it was what really inspired me to apply to midwifery school.”

2025 scholarship applications will be accepted starting in the spring. To learn more, visit the link in our bio.
